Why Owens Corning

OWENS CORNING develops, manufactures and markets insulation, roofing, and fiberglass composites. A Fortune 500® company for 63 consecutive years, the company develops solutions that save energy and improve comfort in commercial and residential buildings. Through its glass reinforcements business, Owens Corning makes thousands of products lighter, stronger and more durable.











