Owens Corning - Wikipedia






















 






Owens Corning

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

Not to be confused with Corning Inc. or Owens-Illinois.

Owens Corning





Type

Public


Traded as
NYSE: OC


Industry
General Building Materials, Composites


Founded
Toledo, Ohio (1938)


Headquarters
Toledo, Ohio, USA



